  74,54,KELLA ‘INNEHU TEDHKIRETUN
  74,55,FEMEN SHA’E DHEKEREHU
  74,56,WE MA JEDHKURUNE ‘ILLA ‘EN JESHA’EL-LAHU HUWE ‘EHLUT-TEKWA WE ‘EHLUL-MEGFIRETI